{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"34729b5f0b","title":"大字报——“取消学校中的党委会、团委会”","origin":"1957年6月13日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c6fde24f0c","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"34729b5f0b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"e31180f0fb","name":"天津大学学生"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d57072042c","type":"title","text":"大字报——“取消学校中的党委会、团委会”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"7c4a38f22a","type":"authors","text":"天津大学学生","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"06e60da38d","type":"appellation","text":"天大一些学生提出带有政治性问题的有：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"3ed3254792","type":"appellation","text":"1、取消学校中的党委会、团委会，由教师和学生组成校务会议来领导学校。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"ddc6f4bf7d","type":"appellation","text":"2、团的干部是政治流氓，团委会应受学生会领导。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"002f71c281","type":"appellation","text":"3、改组人民日报和中国青年报。人民日报应该由全国各党派、人民团体、民主人士参加，而不应由共产党操纵。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"ed49e2506f","type":"appellation","text":"4、在高等学校中不应肃反，发动群众搞肃反刺伤了教师和学生的心灵。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"4f73497721","type":"appellation","text":"5、三大主义的根源是民主集中制。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"e98164248c","type":"appellation","text":"6、宪法是挂羊头卖狗肉，民主是“金鱼缸式”的民主。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"},{"id":"0202789b0f","type":"appellation","text":"7、必修政治课违反信仰自由的政策。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b"}],"page":{"id":"71048ee880","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"34729b5f0b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}